# ==============================================================================
# POSTPILOT GLOBAL TRIVY IGNORE FILE
# ==============================================================================
# Purpose:
# This file suppresses approved Trivy findings across source and image scans.
#
# Used by Cloud Build with:
#   --ignorefile /workspace/.trivyignore
#
# Supported entries:
#   - CVE IDs, for example: CVE-2025-55182
#   - GHSA IDs, for example: GHSA-xxxx-yyyy-zzzz
#   - Trivy IDs, for example: AVD-KSV-0001
#
# Rules:
#   - Add one ID per line.
#   - Lines starting with # are comments.
#   - Only add items after security review.
#   - Prefer upgrading dependencies instead of ignoring CRITICAL/HIGH issues.
#   - Do not use this file for Gitleaks findings. Use .gitleaks.toml instead.
#
# Required context for every active exception:
#   - Reason
#   - Owner
#   - Approval
#   - Expiry or review date
#   - Tracking ticket
# ==============================================================================

# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Temporary Exceptions
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------

# CVE-YYYY-NNNNN
# Reason:
# Owner:
# Approved by:
# Expiry:
# Tracking ticket:

